{"tid":1392239,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要]前線防禦術專區 + 重要貼文合集","createTime":"2019-07-31T16:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:38:37.000Z","uid":164565,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"241411ec4d7e8df1f885ae55d6924b79c48fa664","tid":1392239,"uid":164565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"728錯咗好多野, <span style=\"color: red;\">分散咗人手</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">溝通不足</span>, 同時無裝備<span style=\"color: red;\">無意識反擊嘅人上咗前線</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">唔夠裝備嘅同時又留守咗</span>。<br />\n睇片就會發現, 唔夠裝備時喺大馬路守, 被狗一衝, 就有戰友被捕。仲有個錯誤係班狗放完煙, 暴龍即刻衢入嚟打人, 而好多前線無心理準備去反擊, 最後又有人被捕。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-j9Jd2kl-dY&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-j9Jd2kl-dY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGHd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=a24cddd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-j9Jd2kl-dY&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不被捕</span>不流血, 每個人都唔可以少</strong><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">齊裝</span>先好上前, 同埋要<span style=\"color: red;\">有心理準備D狗會衝嚟襲擊你</span>, 唔反擊就一定會被人捉, 所以<span style=\"color: red;\">要gear時</span>唔該問後面嘅人借。<br />\n2. 一定要<span style=\"color: red;\">組隊行動</span>, 要走嗰時<span style=\"color: red;\">拉埋落單嘅人一齊走</span>。點解我哋71咁成功, 係因為行動夠一致, 裝備足。 <br />\n3. 和理非需要幫手帶<span style=\"color: red;\">浮板, 行李喼, 膠板, 木板, 行山杖</span>, 同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">有重量嘅小物品</span> - <span style=\"color: red;\">保健鐵球</span>。最好有腰包裝小物品。只要你<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係帶違禁品</span>[/red], 就算被狗逗, 都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會有罪</span>。你<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要答狗嘅問題, 無野講</span>, 唔好被狗凶到。毅進狗要貪污華舉證, 好難會入罪。前線好需要你嘅物資。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLDTNrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLDTNrS.jpg&h=83a68f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>防止癲狗衝鋒</strong><br />\n癲狗係以咬死人嘅心態衝入人群, 無人夠佢哋鬥, 最好嘅方法係唔好被佢哋埋到身。<br />\n1. 減速debuff, 用<span style=\"color: red;\">油</span>及<span style=\"color: red;\">波子</span>。當要<span style=\"color: red;\">撒退</span>同時又<span style=\"color: red;\">無路障擋癲狗</span>時用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfwNR01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfwNR01.jpg&h=fef25965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 遠攻, 用有重量而細小嘅野。<span style=\"color: red;\">當癲狗衝緊埋黎時</span>, 請佢哋食狗糧。平時破唔到防, 唔好嘥物資。<br />\n3. 釘板<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4rFO2y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4rFO2y.jpg&h=7b7e75a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>水箭龜</strong><br />\n無野攪到, 只好等天收, 睇佢撞車<br />\n<br />\n目標係形成比較強力嘅防禦陣型, 想走時又安全走到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvuDehj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvuDehj.jpg&h=c76c6f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裝備篇<br />\n[發夢]晏就好多人冇豬嘴就上咗前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378320/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378320/page/1</a><br />\n[最新防具圖鑑&amp;購買連結] 詳解防具 一齊黎砌史詩裝保家衛港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1364591/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1364591/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n意見篇<br />\n[前線心態調整] 我係勇武，我覺得衝，都要目標導向，Objective-Oriented<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378355/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378355/page/1</a><br />\n重申多一次，唔明點解前線要留既請入，前線只會係以下三種情況下徹退。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1373325/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1373325/page/1</a><br />\n [緊急] 你知唔知，場運動就快輸？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378617/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378617/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"169428a13f2d76f7a9bd45e2180a855420d2b365","tid":1392239,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"邊個最唔想成立獨立調查委員會？777、犬同三毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\"